## ğŸ“ How to Use

### Quick Start

1. **Read the guide:**
   ```
   SETTINGS_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md
   ```

2. **See the example:**
   ```
   src/components/settings/GeneralSettingsPageImproved.tsx
   ```

3. **Choose a page:**
   ```
   ProfileSettingsPage (most used)
   ```

4. **Follow patterns:**
   ```
   Replace old code with new components
   ```

5. **Test and commit:**
   ```
   npm run build
   git commit
   ```

### Copy-Paste Patterns

**Before:**
```tsx
<div>
  <label>{label}</label>
  <input type="text" />
  {error && <p className="error">{error}</p>}
</div>
```

**After:**
```tsx
<FormGroup label={label} error={error}>
  <EnhancedInput type="text" />
</FormGroup>
```

